message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as the paper is about sound event detection. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CV, and cs.SY. cs.LG and cs.SI are likely as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach for SED. cs.CV is also possible as the paper uses 3D CNNs for learning inter-channel features. cs.SY is also possible as the paper deals with signal processing and machine learning for SED.
